<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要开始了呢，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="40" />
这场名为<tag a="110" b="8" /><delay20 />
捕虫大赛的战斗<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />战斗的对手？<10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的敌人别无其他，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是你自己<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然都叫做虫子，<delay20 />
但有6条腿的甲虫<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />8条腿的蜘蛛类<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有30～50条腿的多足类等等，<delay20 />
种类丰富多彩哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好像普遍来说，<delay20 />
虫子们的腿都很多呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说起捕虫这件事啊，<delay20 />
就好像恋爱的拉锯战呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />贸然接近，<delay20 />
对方立刻就会逃跑，<delay20 />
要举着捕虫网，慢慢靠近哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像这样，一直接近到<delay20 />
能够得到虫子的距离<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在此时挥下捕虫网哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没错，就好像恋爱<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当然有的时候也会不顺利啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哈哈！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />捕虫大赛只要在规定时间内<delay20 />
抓到尽可能多的
虫子就行啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是说，<delay8 />
就算带着很多事先抓到的虫子，<delay20 />
也是毫无意义的哦。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果想参加捕虫大赛，<delay20 />
只要去和广场上的<colour id="3" />龙克斯<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
搭话就可以了哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />我吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还是放弃参赛吧。<delay20 />
因为虫子<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />长得有点可怕呀。</message>
